  <brief_title>Standard Length Catheters vs Long Catheters in Peripheral Vein Cannulation.</brief_title>
  <acronym>Long&amp;short</acronym>
  <official_title>Standard Length Catheters vs Long Catheters in Peripheral Vein Cannulation. A Randomized Controlled Clinical Trial to Test the Complications.</official_title>
